# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Prettier Ignore Configuration
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
#
# Purpose:
#   Exclude generated artifacts, dependencies, binaries, and temporary files
#   from Prettier formatting.
#
# Design Goals:
#   - conservative universal defaults
#   - cross-language compatibility
#   - avoid formatting generated artifacts
#   - minimize accidental exclusion of source files
#
# Reference:
#   https://prettier.io/docs/ignore
#
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

